ont><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Holy cow, the taunt.</span><hr size=1> Tonight I had the pleasure of someone loaning me a Runed Blade for playing tonight. We were, admittedly, a group of twinks.. all about level 45, hunting in the chief area in Droga. Setup was a cleric, enchanter, two rogues, and two warriors. The other warrior had this Runed Blade, but was only level 44.. the weapon procs at 46.<br>
<br>
I was level 47. :D<br>
<br>
For those that don't know, this is a 26/40 2hs weapon with an effect of Rune III. Rune III is about a 270 point damage abosorbing spell. If you ever want to test the taunt this spell has.. have an enchanter cast it during a fight.<br>
<br>
Once I had this baby in my hands, two things happen: I was doing all the tanking, and I wasn't taking any more damage. With boon on me, I was procing at least once per fight. The taunt on this proc was criminal; even two rogues couldn't get the mob off me. The other warrior had a jade mace / frostbringer combo, and I still had no problems holding agro. All I had for haste was an FBSS and augy.<br>
<br>
If you ever get a chance at one of these blades.. go for it. The proc on this weapon breaks all kinds of rules about agro, and as an added bonus, reduces the damage you take. <br>
<br>
It hurt to give the weapon back to it's owner. :) <p>Xzzy, from the Bristlebane server.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utenakha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tenakha</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/4/01 12:55:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Holy cow, the taunt.</span><hr size=1> Strange, I used one for a bit and almost couldn't force myself to use it my damage and taunt was so low compared to jade mace / jagged long sword at the time. <p>Gorlab 60 Warlord<BR>
